context: Pre and Post Delivery Care,Caesarean Section (C Section),
review: I highly recommend Dr. Nabila Rahman, *** ** *** ** *** **** ************* * ************* ** she's been the most incredible and caring doctor we have ever had. Our story is big, but let me make the long story shor...We travelled from US to India in August 2021 and my wife was 28 weeks, while in US we had been going to the best of Ohio health hospitals Women Physicians in OBGYN and Riverside Methodist Hospital in Dublin, Columbus city in Ohio USA. After staying so long in US and used to the best of medical services, the only concern me and my wife Faiza were having was to find matching counterparts here in India. We were lucky to have found the best bet in Dr. Nabila Rahman to continue to support us through our journey of becoming parents again :).The best part was, we consulted her from US itself before we travelled to India and she made us feel at ease and coordinated with our USA Gynecologist and helped us continue rest of our treatments and took care of our pregnancy and final C-Section surgery at Ovum hospital in Bangalore last week. Though there were couple initial concerns we had in US with early pregnancy scanning reports indicating marginal cord insertion, Dr. Nabila helped us gain confidence by paying keen attention to successive timely scanning reports and guided us with her best advises until our pregnancy successfully completed. Do not want to miss the point that she possesses best of the interpersonal and communication skills and very down to earth and more over she is very approachable, responds to  SMS, Whatsapp messages in case of urgent needs and even if we need any minor clarifications pre and post-delivery. The fact that she can be consulted in multiple hospitals including Ovum, Motherhood and Cloud nine chain of hospitals makes it even more easier and hassle-free to book an appointment at a convenient time. Me and my wife Faiza wish her from the bottom of our heart for her obliging, kind and cooperative services and wish her progressively increasing advancements in her career. Thank you - Arshad & Faiza
reply_text:
Thanku dear Faiza and Arshad for ur valuable feedback!! 
Enjoy parenting ‚≠êÔ∏è

review:
We Hafiza & Touheed would like to thank Dr. Nabila, a Angel sent from Almighty for our help during this pandemic.

We would like to share our 1st baby's experience born on 27th Oct 2020 under the supervision of Dr. Nabila.
We were consulting with other Doctor, after the Covid Test passes positive, Doctor refused to take up the things further, we all were worried and the EDD date was very close, by the grace of God we met Dr. Nabila who was a angel sent by God for our help !

Dr. Nabila took up our case during end of 9th month with Covid Positive. We were so happy and relaxed after her consultation with us.
To be honest every day she used to call us and ask the progress status, whenever we call her she never refused our calls even during night times. 

Under the observation of Dr. Nabila, we under went the COVID test again and passes with "Negative".

We are so lucky to have Dr. Nabila and with all her blessings and Awsum care we are blessed with Baby Girl, Baby & Me both were all fine without having any issues.

The Fee charges, hospitality, Nurses care, Doctor's advice etc.. was mind blowing @Ovum.

We are so happy and proud to recommend Dr. Nabila for any issues related to Pregnancy. 

We Thank you Dr. Nabila and recommend all our relatives and friends to you. :) Thanks again
reply_text: Thanku dear hafiza and Touheed., for such a overwhelming feedback!

review:
I have pcos and I visited doctor Nabila early February and started my treatment (iui) in the month of June and alhumdulillah doctor Nabila educated me the dos and don't and treated me .Doctor Nabila counseled me to improve my mental health and motivated me that everything is possible when Allah wills and mashaallah whatever Doctor Nabila told me everything came true and the doctor was very friendly and was there at every single minute of my doubt to clear it even in the mid nights alhumdulillah. 
Thank you Allah and thank you Doctor Nabila .
I would strongly recommend Doctor Nabila to all those patients who have difficulty in conceiving .

context: Pregnancy care and management,Pre and Post Delivery Care,
review:
We have consulted Dr Nabila for second pregnancy and our history of previous miscarriage and ectopic was worrisome, But Dr Nabila has gives us lot of hope and strength, she has made our journey very pleasant and fearless.  She is approachable, explains every bit from the reports, and open for questions, which is very rare skill from that profession (based on my previous experience). Thanks for showing us so much care and concern. **** **** * **** ******, I value the fact that you are a good listener. I value the fact that your attitude is exceptional. Thank you. The journey of pregnancy is bit scary . But caring doctors like you make it friendly and pleasing.  Nine months of our journey could have been a nightmare without your medical supervision. Thanks for making our journey pleasant with nothing less than a dream come true. Good doctors like you replace the Fear of Illness with Trust in Recovery. 

Thanks a lot :)
